fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.store

Interface DirectWriteStore

  • All Superinterfaces:
    InternalEObject.EStore, PersistentStore
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDirectWriteStore, DirectWriteBlueprintsCacheManyStore, DirectWriteBlueprintsStore, DirectWriteHBaseStore, DirectWriteMapDbCacheManyStore, DirectWriteMapDbIndicesStore, DirectWriteMapDbListsStore, DirectWriteMapDbStore, ReadOnlyHBaseStore

    public interface DirectWriteStore
extends PersistentStore
    A PersistentStore that translates model-level operations into datastore calls.

    Future: An abstraction of DirectWriteStores will be implemented to define a global behaviour. For now, it requires to be re-implemented for handle a specific implementation of a database, but later, these functions will be handled by PersistenceBackend.
